    "controller_support": "full",
    "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/37041eb9195171edd1a73a833dd88337.avif?t=1757470185\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras_big/37041eb9195171edd1a73a833dd88337.avif?t=1757470185 width=800 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tu rol es ser el asistente quirúrgico de un inusual cirujano: Un hombre vendado y temeroso de las criaturas mitológicas que debe operar. Durante cada cirugía, deberás responder rápidamente a sus demandas, entregando herramientas, manteniendo los signos vitales del críptido estables, e incluso cumpliendo absurdas peticiones que van más allá de la medicina. Tu acción o falta de ella, puede definir el rumbo de la cirugía.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/fb051e108292527b937337de73d0ac76.poster.avif?t=1757470185\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/fb051e108292527b937337de73d0ac76.webm?t=1757470185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/fb051e108292527b937337de73d0ac76.mp4?t=1757470185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/4e023c4ebfabd090c4343c06e7d7671d.avif?t=1757470185\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras_big/4e023c4ebfabd090c4343c06e7d7671d.avif?t=1757470185 width=800 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >La sala de operaciones es tan ridícula como el mismo cirujano: Una mezcla clandestina entre un quirófano y una sala de estar. Interactúa con múltiples objetos del entorno, desde bisturís hasta tocadiscos. Cambia la música, revisa estanterías, desinfecta herramientas o incluso, refréscate con una soda de naranja o ingiere medicamentos en esta curiosa sala operatoria.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/82533778f053ba48bdb0f46677052fd2.poster.avif?t=1757470185\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/82533778f053ba48bdb0f46677052fd2.webm?t=1757470185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/82533778f053ba48bdb0f46677052fd2.mp4?t=1757470185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/28342ec6016b472197223d4bfb07a147.avif?t=1757470185\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras_big/28342ec6016b472197223d4bfb07a147.avif?t=1757470185 width=800 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >El cirujano, pese a estar vendado, parece ser omnisciente y será sensible a tus acciones, comportamientos y errores. Recordará si le entregaste la herramienta correcta… o una taza de té en su lugar, se enojará si no pones la música que solicitó y alegrará cuando cumples sus extrañas peticiones. El cirujano lo sabe todo, incluso cuántas veces has abierto Scalpel, Please!. La narrativa varía según tu desempeño y amistad con él, viviendo momentos únicos, nuevas líneas de diálogo y múltiples finales. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/cb4a11ed860113f5e0050917bc5c7a7e.poster.avif?t=1757470185\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/cb4a11ed860113f5e0050917bc5c7a7e.webm?t=1757470185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/cb4a11ed860113f5e0050917bc5c7a7e.mp4?t=1757470185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >¿Serás un asistente ejemplar o el peor error de su carrera? En Scalpel, Please!, todo puede cambiar con una sola acción.</p>",
    "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/37041eb9195171edd1a73a833dd88337.avif?t=1757470185\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras_big/37041eb9195171edd1a73a833dd88337.avif?t=1757470185 width=800 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tu rol es ser el asistente quirúrgico de un inusual cirujano: Un hombre vendado y temeroso de las criaturas mitológicas que debe operar. Durante cada cirugía, deberás responder rápidamente a sus demandas, entregando herramientas, manteniendo los signos vitales del críptido estables, e incluso cumpliendo absurdas peticiones que van más allá de la medicina. Tu acción o falta de ella, puede definir el rumbo de la cirugía.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/fb051e108292527b937337de73d0ac76.poster.avif?t=1757470185\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/fb051e108292527b937337de73d0ac76.webm?t=1757470185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/fb051e108292527b937337de73d0ac76.mp4?t=1757470185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras/4e023c4ebfabd090c4343c06e7d7671d.avif?t=1757470185\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3781770/extras_big/4e023c4ebfabd090c4343c06e7d7671d.avif?t=1757470185 width=800 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >La sala de operaciones e